These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, chess, mah-jongg
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Game   | backgammon | chess | mah-jongg   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, project-manager, nurse
1. the security-guard is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the project-manager is on the far left##1
3. the project-manager is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| Job   | project-manager | security-guard | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, tram, skateboard
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Transport   | trike | skateboard  | tram       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, august
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Birthday    | august    | june     | march |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
House: wooden, cottage, art-deco
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the art-deco house##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the art-deco house is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the wooden house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| House         | cottage | wooden     | art-deco |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, card-games
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Hobby        | card-games | filmmaking      | writing  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

