.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, rose
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Flower   | rose      | balloon-flower     | bellflower    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

