.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, family, sports
1. the fan of trance is the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | disaster | family |

