.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
City: new-york, edinburgh, boston
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, nigerian
1. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| City   | boston    | new-york     | edinburgh   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian | nigerian |

