.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, bongani
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the chaman-smoker is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Cigar    | oliveros | bongani   | chaman        |
| Sport   | skiing    | climbing | weightlifting |

